    <etym xml:lang="ru">Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="sva"
            ><lang/><w>gärs</w><gloss><q>кожица</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                ><lang/><w>garsi</w><gloss><q>кожица</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                    ><w/><gloss><q>скорлупа</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="inh"
                ><lang/><w>kars</w><gloss><q>аркан</q></gloss></mentioned>. Не исключено иранское
        происхождение; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="zkh"><lang/><w>кšyк</w><note type="comment"
                xml:lang="ru"> (из *%iкaršiк%i? <bibl><ref target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                        /><biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"
                > (from *%iкaršiк%i? <bibl><ref target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                        /><biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>)</note><gloss><q>ремень</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">Compare <mentioned xml:lang="sva"><lang/><w>gärs</w><gloss><q>thin
                skin</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                    ><lang/><w>garsi</w><gloss><q>thin skin</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned
            xml:lang="ka"><w/><gloss><q>shell</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="inh"
                ><lang/><w>kars</w><gloss><q>lasso</q></gloss></mentioned>. Iranian origin is not
        excluded; compare <mentioned xml:lang="zkh"><lang/><w>кšyк</w><note type="comment"
                xml:lang="ru"> (из *%iкaršiк%i? <bibl><ref target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                        /><biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"
                > (from *%iкaršiк%i? <bibl><ref target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                        /><biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>)</note><gloss><q>strap</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym>
</entry>
